"title": "8444: honouring God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8444",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Giving the reverence and respect to God which is his due. All God's people have a duty to honour him in every aspect of their lives, while unbelievers and even animals can also honour him.</p>\n<h2>God's people must honour him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:23\">PSA 22:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:6\">MAL 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:1-Mal2:2\">MAL 2:1–2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:22-John5:23\">JHN 5:22–5:23</a></p>\n<h2>Ways of honouring God</h2>\n<h3>By worshipping him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:34\">DAN 4:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:22-Isa43:24\">ISA 43:22–43:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:17\">1TI 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:15-1Tim6:16\">1TI 6:15–6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:8-Rev4:11\">REV 4:8–4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:6-Rev5:14\">REV 5:6–5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9-Rev7:12\">REV 7:9–7:12</a></p>\n<h3>By holy living</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:18-1Cor6:20\">1CO 6:18–6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">ROM 12:1–12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:23\">2CO 8:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1-Eph5:3\">EPH 5:1–5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:7-1Thess4:8\">1TH 4:7–4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:15–1:16</a></p>\n<h3>By keeping the Sabbath and religious feasts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:30\">LEV 19:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:8-Exod20:11\">EXO 20:8–20:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:12-Deut5:15\">DEU 5:12–5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:42\">EXO 12:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:12-Exod31:17\">EXO 31:12–31:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:2\">LEV 26:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:13-Isa58:14\">ISA 58:13–58:14</a></p>\n<h3>By showing kindness to others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:31\">PRO 14:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:12-Deut26:15\">DEU 26:12–26:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:40-Matt10:42\">MAT 10:40–10:42</a></p>\n<h3>By honouring his name and his word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:13-Acts19:17\">ACT 19:13–19:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:17\">JDG 13:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:13\">ISA 26:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:16\">MAL 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:48\">ACT 13:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:1\">2TH 3:1</a></p>\n<h3>By acknowledging him as God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:28-Dan3:29\">DAN 3:28–3:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam6:4-1Sam6:5\">1SA 6:4–6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:20\">ISA 43:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:7\">REV 14:7</a></p>\n<h3>By giving tithes and offerings to him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:9-Prov3:10\">PRO 3:9–3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:1-Deut26:11\">DEU 26:1–26:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:6-Mal3:12\">MAL 3:6–3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:19-2Cor8:21\">2CO 8:19–8:21</a></p>\n<h3>By proclaiming his deeds</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:7\">ISA 63:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:23-1Chr16:26\">1CH 16:23–16:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:3-Ps145:7\">PSA 145:3–145:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:4-Isa12:6\">ISA 12:4–12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:1-Dan4:3\">DAN 4:1–4:3</a></p>\n<h3>By obeying him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:12-Num27:14\">NUM 27:12–27:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:7-Num20:12\">NUM 20:7–20:12</a></p>\n<h2>God honours those who honour him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:27-1Sam2:30\">1SA 2:27–2:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:1-Lev10:3\">LEV 10:1–10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:18\">2CH 26:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:26\">JHN 12:26</a></p>\n<h2>God requires sincerity from those who honour him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:5-Mark7:13\">MRK 7:5–7:13</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:1-Matt15:9\">MAT 15:1–15:9</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:1-Acts5:11\">ACT 5:1–5:11</a></p>\n<h2>All people will ultimately honour God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:17\">JER 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:9\">ISA 60:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:9-Rom14:12\">ROM 14:9–14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:23-Isa45:24\">ISA 45:23–45:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:9-Phil2:11\">PHP 2:9–2:11</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is to be honoured as God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:35\">LUK 9:35</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:22-John5:23\">JHN 5:22–5:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:12-Rev5:13\">REV 5:12–5:13</a></p>",
